REPORTQUERY.TITLE: naznach
REPORTQUERY.SQLTEXT:
with nazn as (select a.history_card, iif(a.ls is not null and a.infused_ls is null and a.solvent_ls is null,ls.title||' '||trim(trailing '.' from trim(trailing '0' from a.dose))||' '||coalesce(un.title,''), a.sol_name)|| coalesce (' ('||a.prim||') ',' ') ||dr.title||' '||count(distinct left(tab.timeon,5)) || ' раз(а)' || coalesce (rf.title,'') LS from doc_nazn_ls a inner join doctab_nazn_ls_priem tab on tab.owner=a.id inner join ref_drugintake dr on a.drugintake=dr.id left join ref_relationship_food rf on a.relationship_food=rf.id left join ref_tradingnames_ln ls on a.ls=ls.id left join ref_units_uniq un on a.doseunit=un.id where a.history_card=:HC group by a.history_card, ls.title, a.dose, un.title,a.sol_name,a.ls,a.infused_ls,a.solvent_ls,a.prim,dr.title,rf.title)
select list(nazn.ls,ascii_char(13)) from doc_reception rec inner join nazn on nazn.history_card=rec.id where rec.id=:HC
